<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.4">
<l>eṉatāviyuḷ kalantaperu nallutavik kaimmā</l>
<l>ṟeṉatāvi tantoḻintē ṉiṉimīḷva teṉpatuṇṭē</l>
<l>yeṉatāvi yāviyunī poḻilēḻu muṇṭaventā</l>
<l>yeṉatāvi yāryāṉār tantanīkoṇ ṭākkiṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For the great good help of [your] mingling wirh my soul I remained</l>
<l>giving my soul in exchange. Now, is there [any] talk of it coming back?</l>
<l>You are the soul of my soul, my father who swallowed the seven groves.</l>
<l>Who is my soul? Who am I? You who gave brought [it] into being by taking [it].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
